.gitignore for a monorepo-style project (frontend/ and backend/)

Secrets & Keys (CRITICAL - DO NOT COMMIT THESE)

----------------------------------------------------------------

Ignore all .env files in all directories

.env
.env.*

Specifically ignore the Next.js local env file

frontend/.env.local

Specifically ignore the backend .env file

backend/.env

----------------------------------------------------------------

Backend (Node.js)

Ignore the dependencies folder

backend/node_modules/

Ignore build output (if you use TypeScript, etc.)

backend/dist/

backend/build/

Frontend (Next.js)

Ignore the dependencies folder

frontend/node_modules/

Ignore Next.js build and cache folders

frontend/.next/

Ignore Next.js static export folder

frontend/out/

General OS & IDE files

Windows

Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

IDEs

.vscode/
.idea/

Log files

.log
npm-debug.log
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*